latestIgtvVideos.title: CELEB STYLE CHEAT: Model Edition🖤
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
“Model Off Duty” is term for the Outfits worn by models on the streets . With the little research I did, it’s basically a mix of neutrals and statement pieces. It’s extremely comfortable and chic at the same time. 
So I recreated few of my favourite looks from my very own wadrobe and so can you! 🤍
.

Look 1 Hailey Baldwin Bieber 
Simple black tank from @forever21 paired with black leather pants from @hm and white sneakers from @zara .
.
.
Look 2 Kendall Jenner 
Paired a blue and strip blouse from GK and white pants from @madamefashions and clear heels
.
.
Look 3 Bella Hadid 
Paired blue denim skirt from @hm  with a simple black tank top from @forever21, layered with @promod denim jacket and black mules from @forever21 .
.
.
Music: For Love
Musician: Jef
#smurecreates @stylemeupwithsakshi .
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: 1 Bodycon Dress, 3 Ways 👗
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Bodycon dresses can be a little challenging to wear ,so I styled it in different wearable ways so it not only enhances your body but makes you feel and look like a boss!💁🏻‍♀️👠 .

Bodycon dress - @forever21 .

Outfit 1 - Brunch/ Day Out 
Wore a shirt from @hm over the dress and some white flats from @myntra .

Outfit 2 - Formal 
Wore the dress under a blazer from @hm and clear heels for a clean look!
.
Outfit 3- Dinner Date
Folded the dress to make a top and paired with white linen pants form @marksandspencerindia and silver accessories! .
.
Ps. I never ever wear dresses because I have always been insecure about my “thunder thighs” but I am glad Styling is making me overcome personal struggles! 
#stylist #delhistylist #sustainablefashion #stylingtips #bodycon #fashion #ootdfashion #styleinspo #styleblogger #f21xme #forever21 #stylebybanichhabra
